summary: This document is an account summary from Fifth Third Bank for a travel rewards credit card covering the period from February 21, 2015, to March 20, 2015. It details the account balance, transactions, payments, and rewards points accrued during this period.
keyFacts: The account had a previous balance of $1,807.99 and a new balance of $993.17.
The total credit limit for the account was $7,000 with an available credit of $6,006.
The minimum payment due was $19.00, with a payment due date of April 17, 2015.
Transactions included payments to various businesses such as Drybar, Mark Menolascino M.D., and Aspen Skiing Co.
The reward points balance on the card was 2,913 as of March 20, 2015.
